data.description: Beautiful 4bdrm/3ba Ranch on a corner lot in a small established neighborhood. New LPV flooring in the living area, dining room and basement. Granite counters, interior paint, light fixtures and remodeled basement bathroom along with new front deck and iron spindles. Kitchen has ceramic tile flooring, large laundry room, and backyard hosts a cozy brick encased firepit with bench. Motivated Seller, BRING OFFER!
